    <div>
      <p begin="00:00:30.566" end="00:00:34.547">&#65279;&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:00:47.094" end="00:00:50.333" region="top"> Year 6 of the AIDS epidemic. </p>
      <p begin="00:00:54.729" end="00:00:59.496" region="top"> Greenwich Village, New York City.<br/>The epicenter. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:07.024" end="00:01:12.496" region="top"> With no drugs to treat the disease,<br/>AIDS is nearly 100% fatal. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:12.496" end="00:01:16.369" region="top"> Panic drives a backlash<br/>of blame and anti-gay violence. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:16.369" end="00:01:19.243" region="top"> Even hospitals<br/>routinely turn away the dying. $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:26.040" end="00:01:28.702" region="top"> Fighting for their lives,<br/>patients and their advocates $$</p>
      <p begin="00:01:28.702" end="00:01:30.902" region="top"> take matters into their own hands. </p>
      <p begin="00:01:31.535" end="00:01:34.312">- Welcome to ACT UP. We are <br/>the AIDS Coalition</p>
      <p begin="00:01:34.312" end="00:01:36.541">- [together] to unleash power.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:36.541" end="00:01:39.951">A diverse, non-partisan group<br/>and individuals united in anger</p>
      <p begin="00:01:39.951" end="00:01:42.002">and committed to direct action</p>
      <p begin="00:01:42.002" end="00:01:44.025">-[together] to end the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:44.025" end="00:01:51.562">- In less than 12 hours from now,<br/>we are gonna be taking over City Hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:01:51.854" end="00:01:54.008">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:54.008" end="00:01:55.727">[Crowd chanting]</p>
      <p begin="00:01:55.727" end="00:01:57.992">- [Ed Koch] Yes.<br/>- *[male reporter] Mr. Mayor,</p>
      <p begin="00:01:57.992" end="00:01:59.160">in campaigning <br/>for the lesbian and gay vote,*</p>
      <p begin="00:01:59.160" end="00:02:01.961">in an election year, a bit of<br/>historical context is necessary</p>
      <p begin="00:02:01.961" end="00:02:04.059">in dealing with the AIDS crisis<br/>in New York City.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:04.059" end="00:02:06.111">It wasn't until 1983 that you met</p>
      <p begin="00:02:06.111" end="00:02:08.177">with people to deal with<br/>the AIDS crisis.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:08.177" end="00:02:09.383">How do you respond to these questions?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:09.383" end="00:02:10.559">- [Ed] That it's a falsehood.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:10.559" end="00:02:13.312">- Please, anybody who's<br/>thinking about being arrested,</p>
      <p begin="00:02:13.312" end="00:02:17.844">*fill out a support sheet, make sure<br/>your support person knows who you are*</p>
      <p begin="00:02:17.889" end="00:02:20.094">and what group you're in.<br/>Yeah?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:20.263" end="00:02:25.748">- Um, if we end up in The Tombs,<br/>is there like a queer tank there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:25.748" end="00:02:28.748">and would you recommend that we<br/>ask to be there?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:28.748" end="00:02:31.332">- There is a homo tank<br/>and I've been there</p>
      <p begin="00:02:31.332" end="00:02:33.680">and it's better than the straight tank,<br/>let me tell you.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:33.680" end="00:02:34.845">- [Ed] Who else? Yes?</p>
      <p begin="00:02:34.845" end="00:02:38.504">- [reporter] In the past,<br/>you've described ACT UP as fascist</p>
      <p begin="00:02:38.504" end="00:02:40.575">yet in the press release, <br/>you called them concerned citizen.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:40.575" end="00:02:43.051">*I was wondering <br/>what changed your mind?*</p>
      <p begin="00:02:43.051" end="00:02:45.649">- [Ed] I don't think <br/>that you can't use both.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:45.649" end="00:02:48.402">Fascist can be concerned citizens.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:49.539" end="00:02:55.706">And I don't believe they are fascist.<br/>I think they have used the fascist tactic.</p>
      <p begin="00:02:55.706" end="00:03:00.155">- Let us celebrate together<br/>tonight, the end of the last day</p>
      <p begin="00:03:00.155" end="00:03:02.463">on which Ed Koch can tell himself</p>
      <p begin="00:03:02.463" end="00:03:06.097">that the communities which are <br/>being decimated by this epidemic</p>
      <p begin="00:03:06.097" end="00:03:09.331">are so weak and so divided <br/>among themselves</p>
      <p begin="00:03:09.331" end="00:03:12.012">that he can keep serving us<br/>this kind of bullshit.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.012" end="00:03:12.786">[laughter]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:12.848" end="00:03:15.527">Tomorrow morning, he will begin<br/>to learn the truth.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:15.527" end="00:03:17.217">[applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:03:18.131" end="00:03:21.687">- [Female voice] ACT UP, stand tall<br/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:21.687" end="00:03:25.640">- [Crowd] ACT UP, stand tall<br/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:25.640" end="00:03:29.482">ACT UP, stand tall,<br/>tomorrow morning at city hall.</p>
      <p begin="00:03:29.482" end="00:03:31.303">ACT UP, stand tall...</p>
      <p begin="00:03:31.303" end="00:03:34.917">&#9834; [Music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:03:39.508" end="00:03:41.562" region="top"> City Hall </p>
      <p begin="00:04:02.932" end="00:04:05.814">*- [male reporter] We're talking <br/>to Jim Eigo*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:05.814" end="00:04:08.911">*for the Treatment Issues Committee<br/>of ACT UP.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:08.911" end="00:04:10.269">Jim, what specific treatment issues</p>
      <p begin="00:04:10.269" end="00:04:12.766">are pretty important <br/>in this demonstration this week?</p>
      <p begin="00:04:12.766" end="00:04:16.133">*- [Jim Eigo] The municipal hospitals<br/>are totally falling apart.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:16.133" end="00:04:19.049">*More than half the people<br/>who get diagnosed with AIDS today*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:19.049" end="00:04:22.428">*get diagnosed in the emergency rooms<br/>of our city.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:22.428" end="00:04:24.561">You're going to find yourself <br/>waiting four days</p>
      <p begin="00:04:24.561" end="00:04:27.408">in an emergency room before<br/>you get a bed.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:27.678" end="00:04:31.664">- I'm pretty scared about being <br/>HIV positive.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:31.718" end="00:04:33.304">I don't have much choice in the matter.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:33.304" end="00:04:34.526">- I just love all these people</p>
      <p begin="00:04:34.526" end="00:04:37.250">and I think that what we're <br/>doing is really right.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:37.250" end="00:04:40.554">And -- I mean, listen to this <br/>and look at our people,</p>
      <p begin="00:04:40.554" end="00:04:42.204">it's just really wonderful</p>
      <p begin="00:04:42.204" end="00:04:44.078">and it's worth putting<br/>*ourselves on the line. *</p>
      <p begin="00:04:44.078" end="00:04:46.289">- *[Ann Northrop] There is<br/>no accurate diagnosis.*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:46.289" end="00:04:48.248">*There are incentives<br/>in the city hospitals*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:48.248" end="00:04:50.269">*not to diagnose people with AIDS,*</p>
      <p begin="00:04:50.269" end="00:04:52.852">and therefore people don't get treated.</p>
      <p begin="00:04:52.852" end="00:04:56.259">We are angry at the way this city<br/>has handled this crisis</p>
      <p begin="00:04:56.259" end="00:04:59.837">and we demand that Ed Koch<br/>exert leadership</p>
      <p begin="00:04:59.837" end="00:05:02.417">and declare a state of emergency.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:02.440" end="00:05:03.823">[Applause]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:03.823" end="00:05:07.052">*- [Peter] Go on the street now or wait,<br/>those are the options.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:07.052" end="00:05:08.678">One. He says go.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:08.678" end="00:05:09.687">*-Two, now.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:09.687" end="00:05:10.845">-He says now, three.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:11.122" end="00:05:11.920">
        <span tts:fontStyle="italic">Don?</span>
      </p>
      <p begin="00:05:12.136" end="00:05:13.164">*Go now--*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:13.164" end="00:05:14.923">*-[Reporter] I'm standing here<br/>with Larry Kramer*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:14.977" end="00:05:17.354">*What is ACT UP trying to say today<br/>to Ed Koch?*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:17.354" end="00:05:19.570">-We're sending a message<br/>to public officials,</p>
      <p begin="00:05:19.570" end="00:05:23.314">to closeted public officials<br/>that we won't be shot down anymore</p>
      <p begin="00:05:23.314" end="00:05:25.212">and obviously all the AIDS issues.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:25.212" end="00:05:27.433">*-I would love to see, like,<br/>more cameras or something *</p>
      <p begin="00:05:27.433" end="00:05:29.192">you know, for our own protection.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:29.192" end="00:05:30.536">*-[male voice] and everyone here <br/>has concerns--*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:30.536" end="00:05:32.997">*-[Larry] People die everyday.<br/>Friends get sick everyday.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:32.997" end="00:05:35.365">*I don't--it's like being in the trenches.*</p>
      <p begin="00:05:35.365" end="00:05:38.933">*There's such anger in the community<br/>and that it's coalescing in a way *</p>
      <p begin="00:05:38.933" end="00:05:41.415">that has never been done before.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:41.415" end="00:05:43.220">- Okay, which way do we face girlfriends?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:43.220" end="00:05:45.102">This way or that way?</p>
      <p begin="00:05:45.102" end="00:05:47.146">[crowd talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:49.167" end="00:05:51.128">[cars honking]<br/>[crowd cheering and rallying]</p>
      <p begin="00:05:51.128" end="00:05:53.989">[together] HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:54.081" end="00:05:57.693">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:05:57.693" end="00:06:01.181">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:01.181" end="00:06:04.895">HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.<br/>HEALTHCARE IS A RIGHT.</p>
      <p begin="00:06:04.938" end="00:06:06.912">- [police officer talking]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:06.927" end="00:06:11.352">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:14.174" end="00:06:16.412">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:06:46.178" end="00:06:49.314">[crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:06:49.413" end="00:06:52.436">&#9834; [music] &#9834;</p>
      <p begin="00:07:15.077" end="00:07:18.061">$ How To Survive A Plague. $</p>
      <p begin="00:07:27.245" end="00:07:29.787">- I guess, I'm feeling pretty hopeless<br/>at the moment.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:29.787" end="00:07:36.845">I think that the biggest question that<br/>I'm facing now is how to remain hopeful</p>
      <p begin="00:07:36.845" end="00:07:39.768">in the face of increasing loss.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:40.198" end="00:07:42.992">- *[David Barr] I don't know,<br/>maybe it sounds really corny *</p>
      <p begin="00:07:42.992" end="00:07:43.837">but I--</p>
      <p begin="00:07:46.633" end="00:07:50.405">as difficult as the time is for us,</p>
      <p begin="00:07:52.121" end="00:07:59.470">I like being alive. And I love my friends <br/>and I love my family.</p>
      <p begin="00:07:59.530" end="00:08:04.070">*I love people around me.*<br/>- This, I'm gonna die from this.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:04.108" end="00:08:08.684">This isn't gonna be cured for<br/>years and years and years and years.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:08.684" end="00:08:10.320">*- Doctor's office?*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:10.320" end="00:08:11.878">- [speaking in the phone] <br/>Hi, it's Peter Staley.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:11.878" end="00:08:13.820">It's like living in a war.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:13.820" end="00:08:17.393">All around me,<br/>friends are dropping dead.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:17.517" end="00:08:21.166">And you're scared for your own life<br/>all at the same time.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:23.539" end="00:08:27.245">*I was diagnosed with AIDS-related complex*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:27.245" end="00:08:30.539">*while I was working as a bond trader<br/>on Wall Street.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:30.847" end="00:08:32.676">*I had night sweats.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:32.676" end="00:08:37.644">*I began to get dry, patchy, scaly,<br/>itchy skin on my face. *</p>
      <p begin="00:08:37.727" end="00:08:40.208">*And I would get sick constantly.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:40.208" end="00:08:43.221">*Colds would lay me up for weeks.*</p>
      <p begin="00:08:43.798" end="00:08:47.524">I started to look around in desperation</p>
      <p begin="00:08:48.178" end="00:08:56.086">for ways that I could find treatments<br/>to help save my life.</p>
      <p begin="00:08:58.852" end="00:09:03.830">And there was nothing coming out of our<br/>government's efforts, I quickly realized.</p>
      <p begin="00:09:08.705" end="00:09:13.930">*Everything I read said I had about<br/>two years to live, at most. *</p>
      <p begin="00:09:16.082" end="00:09:19.391">[Crowd shouting]</p>
      <p begin="00:09:20.129" end="00:09:22.315">$ ACT UPS first protest<br/>March 24, 1987 $</p>
      <p begin="00:09:22.315" end="00:09:24.169">*-[male voice] WHAT DO WE WANT?*<br/>*-[crowd answering] A CURE!*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:24.169" end="00:09:26.224">*-[male voice] WHEN DO WE WANT IT?*<br/>*-[crowd answering] NOW!*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:26.224" end="00:09:28.653">*-[Peter] I was on my way to work*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:28.663" end="00:09:31.701">*and I got handed <br/>a flier about ACT UP and AIDS.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:31.711" end="00:09:35.913">*My mentor says, "If you ask me,<br/>I think they all deserve to die" *</p>
      <p begin="00:09:35.913" end="00:09:37.932">*"because they took it up their butt."*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:38.191" end="00:09:43.266">*I was deeply closeted and I had to just <br/>stew about it for the rest of the day.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:46.139" end="00:09:48.972">*I got myself to the very next <br/>ACT UP meeting.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:49.085" end="00:09:52.538">*They could just tap into that<br/>immediate anger and get stuff done.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:52.538" end="00:09:55.106">*-[female voice] We need to get approval <br/>on this...*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:55.106" end="00:09:58.608">*This is a non-violent <br/>and quiet kiss-in.*</p>
      <p begin="00:09:58.608" end="00:10:01.514">We will not leave until<br/>the administrator meets with us</p>
      <p begin="00:10:01.514" end="00:10:06.416">and tells us that Saint Vincent's<br/>is willing to make a public statement</p>
      <p begin="00:10:06.416" end="00:10:08.664">condemning gay and lesbian violence.</p>
      <p begin="00:10:08.664" end="00:10:11.630">[crowd cheering and applauding]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:14.666" end="00:10:16.671">- All those in favor?</p>
      <p begin="00:10:18.403" end="00:10:20.515">*-All those oppose?*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:20.762" end="00:10:22.454">[car passing]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:23.741" end="00:10:26.375">*-[male voice] They're coming.*<br/>*You see that right there.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:26.597" end="00:10:29.309">*You've heard of ACT UP,<br/>you've seen our flyers.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:29.309" end="00:10:31.755">*The kiss-in happens tonight.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:31.763" end="00:10:33.614">*-[male voice] ACT UP, FIGHT BACK.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:33.614" end="00:10:36.853">*Take gloves, ACT UP. Woo, woo.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:38.618" end="00:10:40.516">*-[male voice] I'll deal with the camera.*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:40.516" end="00:10:42.948">*-[female voice] Are your own<br/>security guards ever beat people up here?*</p>
      <p begin="00:10:42.948" end="00:10:45.314">[people chattering]</p>
      <p begin="00:10:52.003" end="00:10:55.006">- Members of the mainstream media<br/>were thrown out as we were</p>
      <p begin="00:10:55.006" end="00:10:58.747">earlier on but Steve and I<br/>came back in and we'll bring you</p>
      <p begin="00:10:58.747" end="00:11:00.321">this exclusive footage inside...</p>
      <p begin="00:11:00.321" end="00:11:02.387">- Don't destroy property, <br/>you're destroying property, okay?</p>
      <p begin="00:11:02.387" end="00:11:04.986">- Actually, you've damaged<br/>some human property last week.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:05.039" end="00:11:08.414">- You will not beat up on faggots<br/>and you will not beat up on lesbians</p>
      <p begin="00:11:08.414" end="00:11:11.799">in hospitals in our own community.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:11.799" end="00:11:14.561">- Two gay women were beaten up,<br/>and when her lover came to respond,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:14.561" end="00:11:15.983">*you know the story. *</p>
      <p begin="00:11:15.983" end="00:11:19.290">*And another story was, two gay guys came,<br/>and one was sick with AIDS. *</p>
      <p begin="00:11:19.290" end="00:11:21.473">*The security guard told him <br/>to get the fuck out of here*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:21.473" end="00:11:23.079">*and called him, "Faggot."*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:23.079" end="00:11:25.334">I think if you're gonna work,<br/>especially in Greenwich Village,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:25.334" end="00:11:28.731">you should have some sensitivity training<br/>because we're not gonna have it.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:28.731" end="00:11:31.199">- I'm willing to meet with three people,<br/>the rest of you leave.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:31.275" end="00:11:33.434">[crowd chattering]</p>
      <p begin="00:11:34.179" end="00:11:36.353">- It's unclear how to play it.<br/>My own instinct would be to say,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:36.761" end="00:11:40.267">"We'd be glad to meet with you<br/>when the meeting is over, we'll leave".</p>
      <p begin="00:11:40.581" end="00:11:43.128">Not to leave before the meeting<br/>takes place.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:43.128" end="00:11:44.245">- Gregg?</p>
      <p begin="00:11:44.245" end="00:11:46.967">- We show the kind of power we can have<br/>by immediate action, by sticking together,</p>
      <p begin="00:11:46.967" end="00:11:48.926">by reaching a consensus together.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:48.926" end="00:11:50.899">We should take the same steps,<br/>we should be cool headed.</p>
      <p begin="00:11:50.899" end="00:11:52.498">- I'm gonna take a straw poll, okay?</p>
      <p begin="00:11:52.498" end="00:11:55.011">*And we agreed to leave the waiting room*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:55.011" end="00:11:57.943">*while he met with <br/>three of our representatives,*</p>
      <p begin="00:11:57.943" end="00:12:01.412">*Gregg, Jerry and Neil<br/>in that public space right there.*</p>
      <p begin="00:12:01.473" end="00:12:05.661">And then we would sit around out here<br/>and wait for the outcome.</p>
      <p begin="00:12:06.861" end="00:12:10.504">- *[Peter] So I said, "Enough of this.<br/>This job is going to kill me." *</p>
      <p begin="00:12:10.504" end="00:12:16.817">So I went on disability and decided<br/>to become a full time AIDS activist.</p>
